<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-adorable-dirt-cupcakes-with-worms"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Adorable_Dirt_Cupcakes_with_Worms"></span>Adorable Dirt Cupcakes with Worms <span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p>Here at Ruffles and Rain Boots, I have been sharing creative cupcake recipes and decorations for years. These little treats &#8211; whether full sized or minis &#8211; are my absolute favorite dessert because they&#8217;re so versatile.</p>



<p>With one of the most popular vanilla cupcake recipes on the Internet, you can believe I was asked to make an easy chocolate cupcake recipe! I&#8217;ll pop that below but you could also pick up some pre-made cupcakes to save time. </p>



<p>If you love this idea but can&#8217;t get started right away, save or share this page using the sharing buttons. It will be easier to find when you&#8217;re ready to begin. </p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-description="Perfect for a construction party, Halloween, a garden party, or just because, these dirt and worms cupcakes are a crowd pleasing dessert! And let&#039;s face it - they are SO MUCH FUN! Learn how easy it is to make this fun cupcake idea for boys and party treat. Provided are a chocolate cupcake recipe, a chocolate buttercream frosting recipe, and how to decorate with crushed Oreos." src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;1200&#039;%20height=&#039;1800&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%201200%201800&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Vertical image of 6 cupcakes with cookie crumb dirt and gummy worms on a baking sheet." class="wp-image-71578 perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Dirt-and-Worms-Cupcakes-with-Gummy-Worms-V.jpg" data-srcset="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Dirt-and-Worms-Cupcakes-with-Gummy-Worms-V.jpg 1200w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Dirt-and-Worms-Cupcakes-with-Gummy-Worms-V-200x300.jpg 200w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Dirt-and-Worms-Cupcakes-with-Gummy-Worms-V-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Dirt-and-Worms-Cupcakes-with-Gummy-Worms-V-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Dirt-and-Worms-Cupcakes-with-Gummy-Worms-V-150x225.jpg 150w" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">The colors and textures of these dirt cupcakes are really fun!</figcaption></figure>
</div></div>



<p>As an Amazon Associate, I could earn from qualifying purchases. There could be affiliate links within this article. </p>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-occasions-to-serve-dirt-cupcakes"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Occasions_to_Serve_Dirt_Cupcakes"></span>Occasions to Serve Dirt Cupcakes<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p>These are so cute and can be displayed in so many fun ways. Here are a few we&#8217;ve done: </p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Construction Party: Use a child&#8217;s toy truck and add the completed cupcakes, along with some cookie &#8220;dirt&#8221; to the back of a dump truck placed on the dessert table </li>



<li>Garden Party: Place each cupcake in a mini clay pot or on top of a pair child&#8217;s garden gloves (also good for a party favor) </li>



<li>Halloween Party: Place a <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Halloween-Tombstone-Horrible-Gravestone-Decorations/dp/B0DF1LXTR5?crid=222PDM8XB9YTY&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.Hbm55_e6helgClRlQ-U3W0KZF2tzgRubLpXw3m5bS8dDyy4FAWNq6JIIHnpx6OgnIzHEbMLKEKXa5Z4HTvotxaOrxbX7icoNZxX7dwhfEjD3ikY9xTTF1YQfPvVVrupsVDcZaEkwEjvMgNx4WataZBICmYBfHisC9mx5fvRwtNmKS-2HBkkQXYbYtKIKIHFdaPMtMEPzo4uRSTGe2Rd1ItINU2FJYu8IB_BVPtzUY5LVc9MnQInJOtzKquDFgWELQfgRwajNK-i3rw_u-risVdiD3uV9n9UhBw3usBMUW-4.e2X50WlwjcQea9L8SMDQxgorHsbllLqmKga7D_Oe-fY&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=halloween+grave+pick&amp;qid=1755696553&amp;sprefix=halloween+grave+pick%2Caps%2C205&amp;sr=8-2&amp;linkCode=ll1&amp;tag=rufandraiboo-20&amp;linkId=2c81e517943316ff93614ef677f4f311&amp;language=en_US&amp;ref_=as_li_ss_tl" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">grave and shovel cupcake toppers</a></strong> (we used these) in each cupcake and serve on a slate slab with scattered spider rings or candy eyeballs. </li>



<li>Nature or Camping Party: If you&#8217;re having an outdoors-themed party, these cupcakes are adorable when placed onto a table with mini stuffed forest animals, flowers, twigs, or faux leaves. </li>
</ul>
</div></div>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-ingredients-and-supplies"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Ingredients_and_Supplies"></span>Ingredients and Supplies <span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p>Below, I&#8217;ll put the measurements for 12 cupcakes, but the recipe can be halved or doubled. </p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>12 cooled chocolate cupcakes (recipe below for my <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/lazy-girl-chocolate-cupcake-recipe/">Lazy Girl&#8217;s Chocolate Cupcake Recipe</a></span></strong>)</li>



<li>chocolate buttercream frosting (you can pick up a tub or use my <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/easy-chocolate-buttercream-frosting-recipe/">Chocolate Buttercream Frosting Recipe</a></span></strong>)</li>



<li>28-30 gummy worms</li>



<li>15 Oreo™ cookies (~6-8 Tbsp, crushed)</li>
</ul>



<p>You can also use a piping bag with a 1M tip or a plastic bag with a corner cut off to easily frost the cupcakes. Most of the cake will be covered, so a fancy tip is not necessary. </p>
</div></div>



<p>RELATED READING: <strong><a href="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/boozy-cupcake-recipes-for-your-next-party/">Boozy Cupcake Recipes for Adults</a></strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1200" data-pin-description="Perfect for a construction party, Halloween, a garden party, or just because, these dirt and worms cupcakes are a crowd pleasing dessert! And let&#039;s face it - they are SO MUCH FUN! Learn how easy it is to make this fun cupcake idea for boys and party treat. Provided are a chocolate cupcake recipe, a chocolate buttercream frosting recipe, and how to decorate with crushed Oreos." src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;1200&#039;%20height=&#039;1200&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%201200%201200&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Close up square image of a chocolate cupcake with chocolate buttercream frosting and cookie crumb dirt with gummy worms." class="wp-image-71580 perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S.jpg" data-srcset="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S.jpg 1200w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-300x300.jpg 300w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-150x150.jpg 150w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-768x768.jpg 768w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-500x500.jpg 500w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-96x96.jpg 96w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-200x200.jpg 200w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-320x320.jpg 320w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-480x480.jpg 480w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-720x720.jpg 720w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/worm-cupcakes-dirt-cupcake-recipe-S-735x735.jpg 735w" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Gummy worms make these dirt cupcakes perfect for grave cupcakes for Halloween or fun worm cupcakes for a party!</figcaption></figure>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-how-to-make-dirt-and-worms-cupcakes"><span class="ez-toc-section" id="How_to_Make_Dirt_and_Worms_Cupcakes"></span>How to Make Dirt and Worms Cupcakes <span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2>



<p>Before we get started, we&#8217;ve also made this fun cupcake decorating idea into a full cake. Round, square, and rectangular cakes all work well in the theme.</p>



<p>Below are the instructions to keep this page open and follow along. If you prefer a printable recipe, scroll down. </p>



<p>First, prepare and bake the cupcakes. You will need to let them fully cool before frosting, as the frosting will not firm up on warm cakes.</p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<p>Next, put the Oreo™ cookies into a plastic bag and crush them into very fine pieces. You can use the back of a spoon to get any clumps. </p>



<p>Note: you can opt to remove the frosting from inside the cookies or leave it. Both ways will work. </p>



<p>Make the frosting or scoop tub frosting into a piping bag or plastic zip top bag. Add a swirl of chocolate frosting to the top of each cupcake &#8211; remember, it doesn&#8217;t have to be pretty, as we will be covering most of it. </p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<p>Spoon the crushed Oreo™ cookies onto the frosting of each cake. Use as little or as much as you like but start with each getting 2-3 teaspoons to add to the overall look. </p>



<p>Cut a few of the worms into smaller pieces (halves or thirds). Add one full worm and a partial worm to each cupcake. </p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-more-cupcake-recipes-you-might-like">More Cupcake Recipes You Might Like </h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/campfire-cupcakes/">Amazing Campfire Cupcakes</a></span></strong> &#8211; Oh, my goodness! If you want an over the top kind of party treat, this is just the thing.</li>



<li><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/surprise-cupcakes-birthday-cupcake/">Safe &#8220;Surprise Inside&#8221; Cupcakes</a></span></strong> &#8211; The little ones go CRAZY for these and they are also great for gender reveal parties.</li>



<li><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/maple-bacon-cupcake/">Maple Bacon Cupcake Recipe</a></span></strong> &#8211; Elevate your palette and get WOW&#8217;ed by these treats. These are always a HUGE hit when served.</li>
</ul>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained">
<p>Please Save or Share This Fun Cupcake Recipe Idea for Parties</p>



<p>Your shares are how this site grows and I am sincerely grateful. Please save this to a party ideas pin board or share it with friends or family on Facebook. </p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="1800" data-pin-description="Perfect for a construction party, Halloween, a garden party, or just because, these dirt and worms cupcakes are a crowd pleasing dessert! And let&#039;s face it - they are SO MUCH FUN! Learn how easy it is to make this fun cupcake idea for boys and party treat. Provided are a chocolate cupcake recipe, a chocolate buttercream frosting recipe, and how to decorate with crushed Oreos." src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=&#039;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#039;%20width=&#039;1200&#039;%20height=&#039;1800&#039;%20viewBox=&#039;0%200%201200%201800&#039;%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="Vertical split image of a worm cupcake with Oreo cookie dirt and text which reads worm and dirt cupcakes." class="wp-image-71576 perfmatters-lazy" data-src="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Construction-Party-Cupcake-Dirt-Worm-gummy-V.jpg" data-srcset="https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Construction-Party-Cupcake-Dirt-Worm-gummy-V.jpg 1200w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Construction-Party-Cupcake-Dirt-Worm-gummy-V-200x300.jpg 200w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Construction-Party-Cupcake-Dirt-Worm-gummy-V-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Construction-Party-Cupcake-Dirt-Worm-gummy-V-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Construction-Party-Cupcake-Dirt-Worm-gummy-V-150x225.jpg 150w, https://rufflesandrainboots.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Construction-Party-Cupcake-Dirt-Worm-gummy-V-735x1103.jpg 735w" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">These gummy worm cupcakes are a hit and can be used for so many occasions.</figcaption></figure>
</div></div>


